{"tid":1021654,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲格曾經想簽辛祖","createTime":"2019-02-14T11:27:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T13:54:20.000Z","uid":3454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"aa8e24c56cee164979fb545458ecd3e49b02901c","tid":1021654,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T11:27:49.000Z","msg":"雲格很欣賞英格蘭新星查頓辛祖，當他仍然執教阿仙奴之時，曾經想過把他帶去兵工廠。<br />\n曼城新星查頓辛祖在外借多蒙特之後極速彈起，幫助多蒙特在德甲爭標。<br />\n雲格說他一早已留意到這位新星：「我曾經想簽辛祖，他來自倫敦，當時他在曼城沒有機會落場。他是新一代的好手之一，能夠盤球而且有傲氣，這是成功球員的條件之一。」（<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=ZfEq%2Fo1sgt4RLlfWMFNbDi%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=d59bb647\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.goal.com/zh-hk/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E9%9B%B2%E6%A0%BC-%E6%9B%BE%E7%B6%93%E6%83%B3%E7%B0%BD-%E8%BE%9B%E7%A5%96/1n3uiximbiqqu1jpnhp33a7f3z\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.goal.com%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E9%259B%25B2%25E6%25A0%25BC-%25E6%259B%25BE%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%2583%25B3%25E7%25B0%25BD-%25E8%25BE%259B%25E7%25A5%2596%2F1n3uiximbiqqu1jpnhp33a7f3z&d=ZfEq%2Fo1sgt4RLlfWMFNbDi%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=d30be31b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.goal.com/zh-hk/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E9%9B%B2%E6%A0%BC-%E6%9B%BE%E7%B6%93%E6%83%B3%E7%B0%BD-%E8%BE%9B%E7%A5%96/1n3uiximbiqqu1jpnhp33a7f3z</a>"},{"pid":"f7510e812bc5df911e887990d23d8a13fb38106b","tid":1021654,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T11:31:08.000Z","msg":"爺爺名宿隊就黎可以去哂五大聯賽爭標了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f63a58163467b5a3cdf41a3b1ec969b561a86b","tid":1021654,"uid":34457,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T11:31:51.000Z","msg":"以為香港嗰個"},{"pid":"48cc91e394358326f972e